yle=\"color:rgb(0, 176, 80);\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.mdpi.com/2079-9292/12/6/1365\">Publisher Link</a>]</p><p><span style=\"color:black;\">[8] Kesavan Gunasekaran et al., “Smart Decision-Making and Communication Strategy in Industrial Internet of Things,” </span><em style=\"color:black;\"><i>IEEE Access</i></em><span style=\"color:black;\">, vol. 11, pp. 28222-28235, 2023.</span></p><p>[<a style=\"color:rgb(0, 176, 80);\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/10073531\">CrossRef</a>] [<a style=\"color:rgb(0, 176, 80);\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://scholar.google.com/scholar?hl=en&amp;as_sdt=0%2C5&amp;q=Smart+Decision-making+and+Communication+Strategy+in+Industrial+Internet+of+Things&amp;btnG=\">Google Scholar</a>] [<a style=\"color:rgb(0, 176, 80);\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/10073531\">Publisher Link</a>]</p><p><span style=\"color:black;\">[9] Vishal&nbsp;Kumar&nbsp;Dhanraj,&nbsp;Lokesh&nbsp;kriplani,&nbsp;and Semal&nbsp;Mahajan,&nbsp;”</span> Research Paper onDesktop Voice Assistant,” <i>International Journal of Research in Engineering and Science</i><span style=\"color:black;\">, vol. 10, no. 2, pp. 15-20, 2022. &nbsp;</span></p><p>[<a style=\"color:rgb(0, 176, 80);\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://scholar.google.com/scholar?hl=en&amp;as_sdt=0%2C5&amp;q=Dhanraj%2C++Lokesh++kriplani%2C++Semal++Mahajan%2C++%E2%80%9DResearch++Paper++on++Desktop++Voice++February+&amp;btnG=\">Google Scholar</a>] [<a style=\"color:rgb(0, 176, 80);\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.ijres.org/papers/Volume-10/Issue-2/Ser-3/C10021520.pdf\">Publisher Link</a>]</p>', '2024-10-08', '2024-11-07', '2024-12-01', '2024-12-24', 'uploads/DST/volume-3/issue-4/DST-V3I4P106.pdf', '2025-09-25 09:48:32', '2025-11-17 12:55:38', 'published');
