-align-justify\">[13] Jacob Cohen, “A Coefficient of Agreement for Nominal Scales. Educational and Psychological Measurement,” <em style=\"color:windowtext;\"><i>Educational and Psychological Measurement</i></em>, vol. 20, no. 1, pp. 37-46, 1960.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">[<a style=\"color:rgb(0, 176, 80);\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://doi.org/10.1177/001316446002000104\">CrossRef</a>] [<a style=\"color:rgb(0, 176, 80);\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://scholar.google.com/scholar?hl=en&amp;as_sdt=0%2C5&amp;q=A+Coefficient+of+Agreement+for+Nominal+Scales.+Educational+and+Psychological+++++++++Measurement&amp;btnG=\">Google Scholar</a>] [<a style=\"color:rgb(0, 176, 80);\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://journals.sagepub.com/doi/10.1177/001316446002000104\">Publisher Link</a>]</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">[14] Exsys,\"Exsys Corvid Software for Expert System Development Tool, 2011. [Online]. Available: http://www.exsys.com/exsyscorvid.html</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">[15] J. Richard Landis, and Gary G. Koch,&nbsp;“The Measurement of Observer Agreement for Categorical Data,” <i>Biometrics</i>, vol. 33, no. 1, pp.&nbsp;159-174, 1977.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">[<a style=\"color:rgb(0, 176, 80);\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://doi.org/10.2307/2529310\">CrossRef</a>] [<a style=\"color:rgb(0, 176, 80);\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://scholar.google.com/scholar?hl=en&amp;as_sdt=0%2C5&amp;q=The+Measurement+of+Observer+Agreement+for+Categorical+Data.++++++++++++++++++++++++Biometrics&amp;btnG=\">Google Scholar</a>] [<a style=\"color:rgb(0, 176, 80);\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.jstor.org/stable/2529310?origin=crossref\">Publisher Link</a>]</p>', '2025-01-05', '2025-02-01', '2025-03-03', '2025-03-28', 'uploads/AIR/volume-3/issue-1/AIR-V3I1P101.pdf', '2025-09-25 16:17:1