n&amp;as_sdt=0%2C5&amp;q=Water+Treatment+Operations%3A+Case+study+of+Mada+Water+Works&amp;btnG=\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">Google Scholar</a>] [<a href=\"https://www.isroset.org/journal/WAJES/archive_issue.php?pub_id=385\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">Publisher Link</a>]</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">[5] WHO, <em>Guidelines for Drinking-Water Quality: Incorporating the First Addendum</em>, 4<sup>th</sup> ed., Geneva: World Health Organization (WHO), 2022. </p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">[<a href=\"https://scholar.google.com/scholar?hl=en&amp;as_sdt=0%2C5&amp;q=Guidelines+for+drinking-water+quality%3A+Incorporating+the+first+addendum&amp;btnG=\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">Google Scholar</a>] [<a href=\"https://books.google.co.in/books?hl=en&amp;lr=&amp;id=x3RyEAAAQBAJ&amp;oi=fnd&amp;pg=PR2&amp;dq=Guidelines+for+drinking-water+quality:+Incorporating+the+first+addendum&amp;ots=72-gjtTV84&amp;sig=XjZWHDmx9QFGsDS1Uq4H7ItoDRo&amp;redir_esc=y#v=onepage&amp;q=Guidelines%20for%20drinking-water%20q\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">Publisher Link</a>]</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">[6] Miklas Scholz, <em>Wetland for Water Pollution Control, </em>&nbsp;2<sup>nd</sup> ed., Elsevier, pp. 1–5, 2016. </p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">[<a href=\"https://scholar.google.com/scholar?hl=en&amp;as_sdt=0%2C5&amp;q=Wetland+Systems+to+Control+Urban+Runoff&amp;btnG=\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">Google Scholar</a>] [<a href=\"https://books.google.co.in/books?hl=en&amp;lr=&amp;id=rLXoBgAAQBAJ&amp;oi=fnd&amp;pg=PP1&amp;dq=Water+Quality+Standards,%E2%80%9D+Wetland+Systems+to+Control+Urban+Runoff,+&amp;ots=pJ_VFybo0K&amp;sig=4hES4SKNczRbvIw5s9r3H9Z0BDc&amp;redir_esc=y#v=onepage&amp;q=Water%20Quality%20Standards%2C%E2\" rel=\"noopener