 Study of the Performance Water Distillation Device by using Solar Energy,” <em>Engineering and Technology Journal</em>, vol. 35, no. 6, pp. 653–659, 2017. </p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">[<a href=\"https://doi.org/10.30684/etj.35.6A.14\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">CrossRef</a>] [<a href=\"https://scholar.google.com/scholar?hl=en&amp;as_sdt=0%2C5&amp;q=Experimental+study+of+the+performance+water+distillation+device+by+using+solar+energy%2C&amp;btnG=\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">Google Scholar</a>] [<a href=\"https://www.iasj.net/iasj/download/cd0072dd462d92a5\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">Publisher Link</a>] </p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">[10] Habila Adamu et al., “Development of a Solar Water Distiller and Laboratory Analysis of the Product,” <em>ABUAD Journal Engineering Research Development</em>, vol. 1, no. 2, pp. 211–217, 2018. </p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">[<a href=\"https://scholar.google.com/scholar?hl=en&amp;as_sdt=0%2C5&amp;q=Development+of+a+Solar+Water+Distiller+and+Laboratory+Analysis+of+the+Product&amp;btnG=\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">Google Scholar</a>] [<a href=\"http://repository.futminna.edu.ng:8080/xmlui/handle/123456789/743\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">Publisher Link</a>]</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">[11] M.A. Hassan et al., “Development of a Laboratory-Scale Solar Water Distiller,” <em>International Journal of Scientific Research in Science, Engineering and Technology</em>, vol. 3, no. 5, pp. 39–46, 2017.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">[<a href=\"https://scholar.google.com/scholar?hl=en&amp;as_sdt=0%2C5&amp;q=Development+of+a+laboratory-scale+solar+water+distiller&amp;btnG=\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">Google Scholar<