4] Min Kyung Ahn et al., “Removal of Hardness from Water Samples by a Carbonation Process with a Closed Pressure Reactor,” <em>Water</em>, vol. 10, no. 1, pp. 1-10, 2018. </p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">[<a href=\"https://doi.org/10.3390/w10010054\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">CrossRef</a>] [<a href=\"https://scholar.google.com/scholar?hl=en&amp;as_sdt=0%2C5&amp;q=Removal+of+hardness+from+water+samples+by+a+carbonation+process+with+a+closed+pressure+reactor&amp;btnG=\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">Google Scholar</a>] [<a href=\"https://www.mdpi.com/2073-4441/10/1/54\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">Publisher Link</a>]&nbsp;</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p>', '2023-06-27', '2023-07-20', '2023-08-27', '2023-10-03', 'uploads/MS/volume-1/issue-1/MS-V1I1P101.pdf', '2025-09-25 17:42:53', '2025-11-17 12:55:38', 'published');
