]&nbsp;Bright Yammaha Amoore et al., “Nutrition Education Intervention Improves Medical Students’ Dietary Habits and their Competency and Self-Efficacy in Providing Nutrition Care: A Pre, Post and Follow-Up Quasi-Experimental Study,” <em>Frontiers in Nutrition</em>, vol. 10, 2023. </p><p>[<a href=\"https://doi.org/10.3389/fnut.2023.1063316\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">CrossRef</a>] [<a href=\"https://scholar.google.com/scholar?hl=en&amp;as_sdt=0%2C5&amp;q=Nutrition+education+intervention+improves+medical+students%E2%80%99+dietary+habits+and+their+competency+and+self-efficacy+in+providing+nutrition+care%3A+A+pre%2C+post+and+follow-up+quasi-experimental+study&amp;btnG=\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">Google Scholar</a>] [<a href=\"https://www.frontiersin.org/journals/nutrition/articles/10.3389/fnut.2023.1063316/full\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">Publisher Link</a>]</p><p>[12]&nbsp;Sanjoy Saha et al., “Effects of a Nutrition Education Intervention on Fruit and Vegetable Consumption-Related Dietary Behavioural Factors among Elementary School Children,” <em>Health Education Journal</em>, vol. 79, no. 8, pp. 963-973, 2020. </p><p>[<a href=\"https://doi.org/10.1177/0017896920944421\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">CrossRef</a>] [<a href=\"https://scholar.google.com/scholar?hl=en&amp;as_sdt=0%2C5&amp;q=Effects+of+a+nutrition+education+intervention+on+fruit+and+vegetable+consumption-related+dietary+behavioural+factors+among+elementary+school+children&amp;btnG=\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">Google Scholar</a>] [<a href=\"https://journals.sagepub.com/doi/10.1177/0017896920944421\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">Publisher Link</a>]</p><p>[13]&nbsp;Sagar Raut et al., “Effect of N