https://doi.org/10.1016/j.ijantimicag.2017.07.002\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">CrossRef</a>] [<a href=\"https://scholar.google.com/scholar?hl=en&amp;as_sdt=0%2C5&amp;q=Antimicrobial+resistance+in+West+Africa%3A+a+systematic+review+and+meta-analysis.&amp;btnG=\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Google Scholar</a>] [<a href=\"https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0924857917302741\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Publisher Link</a>]</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">[9] Despina G. Contopoulos-Ioannidis et al., “Pathways for Inappropriate Dispensing of Antibiotics for Rhinosinusitis: A Randomized Trial,” <em>Clinical Infectious Diseases</em>, vol. 33, no. 1, pp. 76–82, 2001. </p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">[<a href=\"https://doi.org/10.1086/320888\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">CrossRef</a>] [<a href=\"https://scholar.google.com/scholar?hl=en&amp;as_sdt=0%2C5&amp;q=Pathways+for+Inappropriate+Dispensing+of+Antibiotics+for+Rhinosinusitis%3A+A+Randomized+Trial&amp;btnG=\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Google Scholar</a>] [<a href=\"https://academic.oup.com/cid/article/33/1/76/317732\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Publisher Link</a>]</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">[10] Christian G. Daughton, and Ilene S. Ruhoy, “Environmental Footprint of Pharmaceuticals: The Significance of Factors Beyond Direct Excretion to Sewers,” <em>Environmental Toxicology and Chemistry</em>, vol. 28, no. 12, pp. 2495-2521, 2010. </p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">[<a href=\"https://doi.org/10.1897/08-382.1\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">CrossRef</a>] [<a href=\"https://scholar.google.com/scholar?hl=en&amp;as_sdt=0%2C5&amp;q=ENVIRONMENTAL+FOOTPRINT+OF+PHARMACEUTICALS%3A+THE+SIGNIFICANCE+OF+FACTORS+BEYOND+DIRECT+EXCRETION+TO+SEWERS&amp;btnG=\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Google Scholar</a>] [<a href=\"https://setac.onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/full/10.1897/0