(20, 4, 'paper_submission', '<h6 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family:Roboto, sans-serif;font-size:1rem;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:1.2;margin:0px 0px 0.5rem;orphans:2;padding:0px;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">Preparation Guidelines for Paper Submission:</h6><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family:Poppins, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px 0px 1rem;orphans:2;padding:0px;text-align:justify;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:50px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\" id=\"head1\">Submissions by anyone other than one of the authors will not be accepted. The submitting author takes responsibility for the paper during submission and peer review.</p><ul style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-family:Poppins, sans-serif;margin:0px 0px 1rem;padding:0px 0px 0px 2rem;\"><li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-family:Poppins, sans-serif;margin:0px;padding:0px;\" data-list-item-id=\"e3ad40e5afae999735c44187a719facf3\">Manuscripts submitted to this journal will be deemed as they have not been published and are not under consideration for publication elsewhere.</li><li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-family:Poppins, sans-serif;margin:0px;padding:0px;\" data-list-item-id=\"eb1c6644e29c363fd728fc146a7149977\">Submit your paper in the form of Microsoft word format ( .doc or .docx ) , if you were used latex software for article preparation then send your paper in PDF format.</li><li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-family:Poppins, sans-serif;margin:0px;padding:0px;\" data-list-item-id=\"ecb17abcb9484c655907ad2bd83dd8b51\">Submitting the paper in multiple journals are offence, don\'t waste our valuable time.</li><li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-family:Poppins, sans-serif;margin:0px;padding:0px;\" data-list-item-id=\"e71ea2640e0ae474dab1541f802ee6c8c\">Once the paper is accepted, it can\'t be withdrawn at any cost.</li><li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-family:Poppins, sans-serif;margin:0px;padding:0px;\" data-list-item-id=\"eb74a69d3951495743b708c90ba0467ce\">Please follow publication ethics and regulation.</li><li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-family:Poppins, sans-serif;margin:0px;padding:0px;\" data-list-item-id=\"ec8f71dc21700cc930896d59c69f5020f\">Avoid plagiarism and copied material.</li><li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-family:Poppins, sans-serif;margin:0px;padding:0px;\" data-list-item-id=\"ec6443b53613c7d1c512da57a86203162\">Strictly follow DS Journals Paper Template.</li></ul><h6 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family:Roboto, sans-serif;font-size:1rem;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:1.2;margin:0px 0px 0.5rem;orphans:2;padding:0px;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">Terms of Submission:</h6><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family:Poppins, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px 0px 1rem;orphans:2;padding:0px;text-align:justify;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:50px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\" id=\"head2\">Papers must be submitted on the understanding that they have not been published elsewhere and are not currently under consideration by another journal published by DS Journals or any other publisher. The submitting author is responsible for ensuring that the article\'s publication has been approved by all the other coauthors. It is also the authors\' responsibility to ensure that the articles emanating from a particular institution are submitted with the approval of the necessary institution.</p><h6 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family:Roboto, sans-serif;font-size:1rem;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:1.2;margin:0px 0px 0.5rem;orphans:2;padding:0px;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">Peer Review:</h6><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family:Poppins, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px 0px 1rem;orphans:2;padding:0px;text-align:justify;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:50px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\" id=\"head3\">All manuscripts are subject to peer review and are expected to meet standards of academic excellence. If approved by the editor, submissions will be considered by peer-reviewers, whose identities will remain anonymous to the authors.</p><h6 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family:Roboto, sans-serif;font-size:1rem;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:1.2;margin:0px 0px 0.5rem;orphans:2;padding:0px;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">Units of Measurement:</h6><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family:Poppins, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px 0px 1rem;orphans:2;padding:0px;text-align:justify;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:50px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\" id=\"head4\">Units of measurement should be presented simply and concisely using System International (SI) units.</p><h6 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family:Roboto, sans-serif;font-size:1rem;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:1.2;margin:0px 0px 0.5rem;orphans:2;padding:0px;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">Title and Authorship Information:</h6><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family:Poppins, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px 0px 1rem;orphans:2;padding:0px;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">The following information should be included:</p><ul style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family:Poppins, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px 0px 1rem;orphans:2;padding:0px 0px 0px 2rem;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\"><li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-family:Poppins, sans-serif;margin:0px;padding:0px;\" data-list-item-id=\"e1584e961fc0d2ac369e776124774d37b\">Paper title</li><li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-family:Poppins, sans-serif;margin:0px;padding:0px;\" data-list-item-id=\"eafe43b580c96f61bdce3d96c2bc8354e\">Full author names</li><li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-family:Poppins, sans-serif;margin:0px;padding:0px;\" data-list-item-id=\"e313ccdf2f0a47399810144d15fe82315\">Full institutional mailing addresses</li><li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-family:Poppins, sans-serif;margin:0px;padding:0px;\" data-list-item-id=\"eb36f83265b79f24b4c57911f6bf66719\">Email addresses</li><li style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-family:Poppins, sans-serif;margin:0px;padding:0px;\" data-list-item-id=\"e012df4a91dd3b7844aecacbe6b79f847\">Abstract</li></ul><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family:Poppins, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px 0px 1rem;orphans:2;padding:0px;text-align:justify;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:50px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\" id=\"head5\">The manuscript should contain an abstract. The abstract should be self-contained and citation-free and should not exceed 200 words.</p><h6 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family:Roboto, sans-serif;font-size:1rem;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:1.2;margin:0px 0px 0.5rem;orphans:2;padding:0px;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">Introduction:</h6><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family:Poppins, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px 0px 1rem;orphans:2;padding:0px;text-align:justify;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:50px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\" id=\"head6\">This section should be succinct, with no subheadings.</p><h6 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family:Roboto, sans-serif;font-size:1rem;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:1.2;margin:0px 0px 0.5rem;orphans:2;padding:0px;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">Materials and Methods:</h6><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family:Poppins, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px 0px 1rem;orphans:2;padding:0px;text-align:justify;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:50px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\" id=\"head7\">This part should contain sufficient detail so that all procedures can be repeated. It can be divided into subsections if several methods are described.</p><h6 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family:Roboto, sans-serif;font-size:1rem;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:1.2;margin:0px 0px 0.5rem;orphans:2;padding:0px;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">Preparation of Tables:</h6><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family:Poppins, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px 0px 1rem;orphans:2;padding:0px;text-align:justify;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:50px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\" id=\"head8\">Tables should be cited consecutively in the text. Every table must have a descriptive title and if numerical measurements are given, the units should be included in the column heading.</p><h6 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family:Roboto, sans-serif;font-size:1rem;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:1.2;margin:0px 0px 0.5rem;orphans:2;padding:0px;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">Results and Discussion:</h6><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family:Poppins, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px 0px 1rem;orphans:2;padding:0px;text-align:justify;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:50px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\" id=\"head9\">This section may each be divided by subheadings or may be combined.</p><h6 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family:Roboto, sans-serif;font-size:1rem;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:1.2;margin:0px 0px 0.5rem;orphans:2;padding:0px;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">Conclusions:</h6><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family:Poppins, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px 0px 1rem;orphans:2;padding:0px;text-align:justify;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:50px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\" id=\"head10\">This should clearly explain the main conclusions of the work highlighting its importance and relevance.</p><h6 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family:Roboto, sans-serif;font-size:1rem;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:1.2;margin:0px 0px 0.5rem;orphans:2;padding:0px;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">Acknowledgments:</h6><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family:Poppins, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px 0px 1rem;orphans:2;padding:0px;text-align:justify;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:50px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\" id=\"head11\">All acknowledgments (if any) should be included at the very end of the paper before the references and may include supporting grants, presentations, and so forth.</p><h6 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family:Roboto, sans-serif;font-size:1rem;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:1.2;margin:0px 0px 0.5rem;orphans:2;padding:0px;text-align:start;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">References:</h6><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family:Poppins, sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px 0px 1rem;orphans:2;padding:0px;text-align:justify;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:50px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\" id=\"head12\">Authors are responsible for ensuring that the information in each reference is complete and accurate. All references should be cited within the text; otherwise, these references will be automatically removed.</p>', 1, '2025-11-14 14:44:15', '2025-11-14 14:57:26'),
